CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

January 30, 2014

[Cite as 01/30/2014 Case Announcements, 2014-Ohio-292.]

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2012-2100. State ex rel. 4445 Ltd. v. Cuyahoga Cty. Bd. of Revision.

In Mandamus and Procedendo. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for writs of mandamus and procedendo.

Upon consideration of i relator’s application for dismissal, it is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
